  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<p>Spark the curiosity in you and understand the inner workings of the pawnbroking/consumer financing business. You will be part of the digitalisation and transformation of the group. Experience accelerated learning through on the ground exposure and have a closer look into the business. Use this opportunity to build your strategic market knowledge and be the forefront of the team that drive digitalisation and change to a traditional business.</p><ul><li>Report directly to Finance in charge</li><li>Collaborate with team from HQ on digitalisation and process improvement</li><li>Liaise with book keepers from all outlets to synchronise/update developments</li><li>Reconcile inventories, receivables and incoming funds via Paynow QR</li><li>Ensure forfeited tickets are fully inventorised or sold</li><li>Learn to access databases to extract data</li><li>Ensure data populated via API are accurate</li><li>Assist in the upkeep and accuracy of data within cloud accounting system</li><li>Support team in daily operation and administrative tasks when needed</li></ul>",
