    "description": "<p>Fund Express provides pawnbroking services, which is a form of collateralised micro-financing involving products ranging from gold ornaments, diamonds and gems jewellery, and selected branded watches. Pawnbroking is a regulated and licensed activity under the Pawnbrokers Act. The Group is also engaged in the retailing of pre-owned jewellery and gold, which complements its pawnbroking business. FE Group has traditionally been offering very attractive valuation by its in-house expert appraisers and providing friendly services and attractive interest rates to its customers that include locals and foreigners from Asia, Europe, and North America. FE Group upholds the highest commitment level and responsibility to its clients and ensure all terms and conditions are explained in detail, understood, and adhered to.</p>",
